items.title: AT+CREG=1
items.description: sets URCs for general attach status

items.title: AT+CEREG=1
items.description: sets URCs for enhanced (LPWA) attach status

items.title: AT+CPIN?
items.description: checks the SIM and PIN was OK

items.title: AT+CFUN=1,1
items.description: reboots the modem and gets online after

items.title: ATI9
items.description: Informs about the modem FW version etc.

items.title: AT+KSRAT?
items.description: Get the Radio Access Network Type

items.title: AT+GNSSNMEA=4
items.description: Modem writes NMEA sentences to UART (exit with +++)

items.title: AT+GNSSCONF?
items.description: This command configures various GNSS configurations such as satellite constellations.
